                  <persName role="owner" ref="PRS0000">The name of the original donor had been erased throughout the Ms. and replaced with those of different persons, like Walda Yoḥannǝs (e.g., <locus target="3ra">3ra</locus>, 9ra, 21va, 25vb, 39va, 45ra) or Gabra Ḥǝywat (e.g., <locus target="13ra">13ra</locus>, 39vb, 43vb, 62ra). These names had been overwritten with those of (Gabra?) Tadewos or (Gabra?) Śǝllāse, which in turn had been crossed out or erased from <locus target="54vb">54vb</locus> onwards and replaced with that of Walda Yodahe (e.g., fols.  61vb, 63ra, 63vb, 64rb, 66rb, 70rb, 89rb, 90ra, 98rb). Walda Yodahe is mentioned as the commissioner in Additio 2.</persName>
